These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
5 different games are played: go, snooker, canasta, billiard, scrabble
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, lemonade, coffee, water
The people have 5 different jobs:  pilot, fisherman, chef, bartender, accountant
 1. the chef is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the accountant is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the fisherman is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the pilot is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the bartender##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the pilot##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is the pilot##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Game   | snooker  | go | canasta | billiard | scrabble  |
| Beverage           | fanta     | water     | coffee  | soy-milk   | lemonade    |
| Job         | chef | bartender    | fisherman | pilot  | accountant |

