.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, motorbike, scooter, bus
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, london, new-york, berlin
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, documentary, family, martial-arts
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, grey, turquise, azure, lilac
 1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 2. the person who likes turquise is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person who likes azure is the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
13. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Transport          | motorbike        | bus | car     | scooter      | quad-bike  |
| City           | san-francisco   | london | berlin    | new-york | edinburgh |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family     | martial-arts | adventure    | animation  |
| Color   | azure     | grey | purple    | lilac      | turquise    |

