.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, r&b, hip-hop, country, soul
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, october, may, march, july
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, dahlia, iris, sunflower
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of punk##1
13. the fan of country is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre      | country          | hip-hop  | r&b       | punk     | soul      |
| Birthday         | october | july | march  | may   | november    |
| Flower   | tulip        | sunflower | marigold | iris    | dahlia   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

