.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, lily, daisy, azalea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, badminton, biathlon, surfing
City: hamburg, miami, boston, paris, berlin
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
10. the person who growsazalea is the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Flower          | daisy        | iris       | lily | aconite   | azalea  |
| Sport   | surfing | badminton | snowboarding | lacrosse   | biathlon |
| City   | paris         | berlin     | miami | hamburg | boston     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

