.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower, nectarine, potato, pumpkin
5 different games are played: go, billiard, canasta, mah-jongg, domino
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, american, polish, french, japanese
House: colonial, cape-cod, tower, craftsman, farmhouse
 1. the american is the tower house##1
 2. the tower house is the person playing canasta##1
 3. the person playing domino is on the left of the american##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person playing go is the colonial house##1
 7. the thai is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the japanese is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the american##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the polish##1
12. the craftsman house is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Food          | cauliflower    | pumpkin  | nectarine | asparagus    | potato      |
| Game           | domino | canasta | go  | mah-jongg | billiard |
| Nationality   | polish           | american      | japanese      | french        | thai     |
| House         | cape-cod         | tower  | colonial   | craftsman       | farmhouse  |

