.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, iris, zinnia, rose
5 different games are played: scrabble, chess, billiard, domino, go
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish, hamster, snake
There 5 different types of food: pineapple, pepper, banana, garlic, nectarine
 1. the person eating pineapple is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the person playing billiard is the person eating banana##1
10. the person playing go is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person playing go##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person eating banana##1
14. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
| Flower      | balloon-flower        | zinnia   | amaryllis  | iris         | rose |
| Game   | chess   | scrabble   | go | domino      | billiard   |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish   | snake   | ferret        | hamster  |
| Food         | pineapple   | pepper | garlic | nectarine | banana  |

