 4. the person traveling to hamburg is the colonial house##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the colonial house is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person eating broccoli is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
10. the gothic-revival house is the person eating artichoke##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is the fan of folk##1
12. the victorian house is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the palace house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
14. the person eating lemon is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
