.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, juice, milk
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, orchid, aconite, rose
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, taxi, bike, bus
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, russian, japanese, chinese, egyptian
 1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 4. the russian is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the japanese is on the right of the russian##1
 7. the person who growstulip is the thai##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the chinese is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
12. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Flower   | orchid  | aconite | tulip | daffodil  | rose  |
| Transport   | bike    | jet-ski    | car        | bus | taxi     |
| Nationality           | russian | japanese      | thai       | chinese   | egyptian   |

