.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis, tulip, daffodil, orchid
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, april, january, october, february
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, vegafina, dunhill, oliveros, game
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who growstulip is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the vegafina-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the swisher-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | daffodil | tulip  | orchid    | daisy |
| Birthday   | october     | february     | april | december      | january      |
| Cigar           | dunhill       | swisher     | vegafina     | game     | oliveros   |
| Sport         | basketball | swimming | rowing  | volleyball | sailing   |

