.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, climbing, biathlon, rugby, volleyball
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, security-guard, freelancer, doctor, writer
There 5 different types of food: watermelon, potato, eggplant, spinach, asparagus
 1. the security-guard is on the left of the doctor##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating potato is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the freelancer##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is in the middle##1
10. the writer is on the right of the freelancer##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking tea##1
13. the doctor is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Beverage      | lemonade | tea    | cola   | milk   | coffee |
| Sport   | tennis    | biathlon   | volleyball | rugby | climbing  |
| Job           | security-guard     | doctor | freelancer   | writer | teacher   |
| Food     | potato  | asparagus   | watermelon    | spinach   | eggplant |

