.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, black, pink, apricot, emerald
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bluemaster, swisher, aristoff, montecristo
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, video-games, singing, puzzles, cooking
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the person who likes white is the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who likes pink is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1
13. the davidoff-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | milk    | cola       | sprite |
| Color   | pink           | black   | emerald   | apricot       | white  |
| Cigar   | bluemaster       | davidoff | swisher | aristoff     | montecristo   |
| Hobby     | singing    | video-games   | puzzles   | filmmaking | cooking   |

 